<plot>Neil and Suze are two rascally fourth grade detectives who spy on their cantankerous teacher, Sister Mary Myrna. Feeling picked on in class, Neil and Suze retaliate by nosing into Sister's private life. Covert investigations, "expert" spy techniques, vengeful behaviors, snide classmates, and an unfair teacher all contribute to a fun and serious film on growing up.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?392516</url></doc>
